      "text": "Prototype Design Pattern",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Prototype Design Pattern",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "7vrlRuFF_YDMKN9BcU--r",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 504.6600034302569,
      "y": -36.19984898290974,
      "width": 1027.939208984375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 168296810,
      "version": 315,
      "versionNonce": 983502383,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781896787842,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When Object Creation is Very high time consuming and expensive like complex calculation or db connection \nso instead of creating it just clone it!!! ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When Object Creation is Very high time consuming and expensive like complex calculation or db connection \nso instead of creating it just clone it!!! ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_EWnyB5c3PPGV7I0QeyhZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 509.8051393514345,
      "y": 34.15655830578925,
      "width": 876.6848996009354,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1170753770,
      "version": 435,
      "versionNonce": 826733391,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781896792893,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Like Chess Keys or Game NPCs multiple Npc, Taking more time and memory consuming of\nObject Creation.\n\nSo instead, Clone Or Copy the Object",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Like Chess Keys or Game NPCs multiple Npc, Taking more time and memory consuming of Object Creation.\n\nSo instead, Clone Or Copy the Object",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0L06u7UFCQacF4SAuelWj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 528.1893318371895,
      "y": 427.00211119040466,
      "width": 903.859375,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 847367478,
      "version": 340,
      "versionNonce": 124489775,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781895018120,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We use the copy constructor to handle this or or or in Cpp or in Java or in C# we have the \nIClonable interface that helps us to override the clone method \\\n\nSee the codewith durgesh Prototype Videos all Deep Copy and Shallow Copy walaa bhi!!!",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We use the copy constructor to handle this or or or in Cpp or in Java or in C# we have the \nIClonable interface that helps us to override the clone method \\\n\nSee the codewith durgesh Prototype Videos all Deep Copy and Shallow Copy walaa bhi!!!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
