      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781943717804,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "in cpp and \nin java we already have \nIClonable interface wejust need to \nimplement our concreat class with IClonable\nin concreat class we can override the \nclone method or just use \nthe default clone method provided\nby IClonable simple ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "in cpp and \nin java we already have \nIClonable interface wejust need to \nimplement our concreat class with IClonable\nin concreat class we can override the \nclone method or just use \nthe default clone method provided\nby IClonable simple ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "oQj5lisPF8CC-UKRSKhCK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 506.49621693058816,
      "y": 3369.780945511362,
      "width": 1112.331537155878,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1857699318,
      "version": 726,
      "versionNonce": 2051547405,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782134739275,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Prototype design pattern just helps us to clone or copy the another instance simple!!!\n\n\nUsecases:\nNPCs in games like GTA, creating multiple objects which require same expensive operations like connecting to same\nDB or computing some value",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Prototype design pattern just helps us to clone or copy the another instance simple!!!\n\n\nUsecases:\nNPCs in games like GTA, creating multiple objects which require same expensive operations like connecting to same DB or computing some value",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
